      <p class="title"><b>PREPARATION:</b></p>
      <li><b>1.</b> Add 4 tbsp oat to half a cup of (125 ml) milk and let it sit overnight in the fridge.</li>
      <li><b>2.</b> Next day, put the oats, half a cup of (125ml) milk and 1/2 frozen banana in a blender and blend.</li>
      <li><b>3.</b> Take the mixture on the serving plate. (You can add more milk according to its consistency).</li>
      <li><b>4.</b> Put on the top of it, 1/2 apple, 1/2 banana, and chopped raw almonds.</li>
      <li><b>5.</b> Mix carob exract with tahini and pour it over.</li>
      <li><b>6.</b> As a final touch, sprinkle with grated nutmeg on it.</li>
</div>
